<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1435,1961,2026]" lastBlockId="3.[151,1437,152,1222]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="50" pageId="1" pageNumber="48">Pale brown with green tinge. Head olivaceous; ocelli margined by brown to dark brown; spot between inner margin of eye and ecdysial line on vertex brown; lower marginal area of face light brown. Few irregular spots on anterior margin of pronotum and scutellum pale brown. Forewing venation brown, few apical cross veins, apices of claval veins and claval apex dark brown. Pro and meso-thoracic legs with brown patches on coxae, trochanter, femur and tibiae especially on lower surface; tarsi pale greenish yellow; bases of hind tibial spines dark brown.</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/190679/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="49" targetBox="[182,1436,188,1898]" targetPageId="2">
